faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每個月$5X 飲少杯咖啡姐 我都唔記得支持幾耐 信用卡自動扣數"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T14:50:40.000Z","msg":"每月五十幾蚊都要擔心支持得幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋個所謂市場，根本就比支那扭曲晒，有幾多公司就係因為驚得罪支那而唔敢落廣告"},{"pid":"f114bd1829354fe928913b9b801ec8b57c6f2b18","tid":1935283,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b39456d522d66f29d16b807236ab1b1f7d3a2c4f","tid":1935283,"uid":30001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b525e290cf3409dc82d0ea6fa8f826e281752576","tid":1935283,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f066f6ef977ded8a17855b6f36f1c81c49716f90","tid":1935283,"uid":192732,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T12:46:45.000Z","msg":"你支持得幾耐，根本佢唔改革就會被市場淘汰<br />\n<br />\n更唔好講佢訂閱根本唔係主要收入來源"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T12:47:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每個月$5X 飲少杯咖啡姐 我都唔記得支持幾耐 信用卡自動扣數"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T14:50:40.000Z","msg":"每月五十幾蚊都要擔心支持得幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋個所謂市場，根本就比支那扭曲晒，有幾多公司就係因為驚得罪支那而唔敢落廣告"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T14:51:45.000Z","msg":"I mean 唔知join 左幾耐plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1,2,3年果種"}]}